336
00:16:41,654 --> 00:16:44,553
Azimat kamu tak penting sekarang ini.

337
00:16:44,554 --> 00:16:48,053
Betul juga.

338
00:16:48,054 --> 00:16:52,153
Bercakap tentang azimat... Ada sesuatu yang pelik.

339
00:16:52,154 --> 00:16:55,053
