341
00:16:59,254 --> 00:17:02,953
tapi telefon dan rokoknya juga disimpan di dalam poket yang sama

342
00:17:02,954 --> 00:17:06,153
sehingga poketnya kembung.

343
00:17:06,154 --> 00:17:07,553
Kenapa agaknya

344
00:17:07,554 --> 00:17:11,053
dia simpan begitu banyak barang di dalam satu poket?

345
00:17:11,054 --> 00:17:13,553
Mungkin kerana tangan kiri dia berbalut.

346
00:17:13,554 --> 00:17:16,053
Memandangkan pergelangan tangan kiri Encik Kunimatsu retak,

347
00:17:16,054 --> 00:17:19,153
dia mungkin hanya boleh gunakan tangan kanannya.

348
00:17:19,154 --> 00:17:24,153
Saya faham. Itulah sebabnya dia hanya boleh gunakan poket sebelah kanan.

349
00:17:24,154 --> 00:17:28,753
Tapi poket kanan jaket dia kosong.

350
00:17:28,754 --> 00:17:31,553
Adakah kamu pasti Encik Kunimatsu telah pergi

351
00:17:31,554 --> 00:17:34,253
