356
00:17:45,554 --> 00:17:47,754
jika kita menyoal mereka bertiga.

357
00:17:48,954 --> 00:17:51,353
Jika ini bukan jenayah terancang,

358
00:17:51,354 --> 00:17:52,753
si pelaku mungkin

359
00:17:52,754 --> 00:17:55,453
